# H: position in the spectrum
# S: color saturation ("purity")
# V: color brightness

def rgb_to_hsv(r, g, b):
    maxc = max(r, g, b)
    minc = min(r, g, b)
    rangec = (maxc-minc)
    v = maxc
    if minc == maxc:
        return 0.0, 0.0, v
